data.description: This home has new flooring 2022, carpet upstairs and LVP down. Painted in 2022. Home is conveniently located near the interstate, downtown Norfolk, Norfolk Zoo, waterside district and shopping so new homeowner can enjoy all of the restaurants, bars, shops, and views Norfolk as to offer. The home offers an open style floor plan and features a spacious living room, open kitchen with pantry, 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and half bath downstairs, covered porches out back and front, oversized backyard, and a wide 1 car garage. Laundry is upstairs with all the bedrooms. Primary room has an ensuite and large walk in closet. BRING ANY AND ALL OFFERS. HIGHLY motivated sellers.
